{"tid":1567963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[淘大] 過左三個月, 仲係未識流水抗爭","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:07:11.000Z","uid":59887,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f11cff868567dcd468fa0f43220832975d7f31","tid":1567963,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"淘大擺明係局<br />\n藍絲popo黑社會擺到明吹大雞大集結<br />\n又唔係夠人就去玩反包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得果幾十個手足就吹雞去同人硬撼<br />\n依加咪見一個拉一個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地去佔商埸咪尤佢地佔囉<br />\n見唔見d舖落哂閘呀？ 我地多謝佢地都黎唔切啦<br />\n<br />\n人進我退 明知送頭都仲死衝去唔係叫勇武<br />\n睇清楚形勢先好叫人衝啦 好嗎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔啱聽我都要講 話我冷氣又好 要block隨便<br />\n915見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4518053009bcab5f54eef00631adaf7510cc74","tid":1567963,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bdeb7eea0b070b9d9fda2054a53054eedc599fe","tid":1567963,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}